    <h3>Create your account</h3>
    <p><strong>If you have <code>ALLOW_SIGNUP=true</code> in your env vars you'll see a signup box on the edit page. If not, you'll need to add it.</strong></p>
    <p><strong>When you sign up the signup box will go away and only a login box will remain, because there's a <code>SIGNUP_LIMIT=1</code> by default (so you don't have to restart your server).</strong></p>
    <p><strong>After your account is created you'll be redirected to the editor and can view and edit this doc!</strong></p>
